This is IdleRPG v3.1.3

This is based on v3.1.2 by jotun but contains many of the patches and updates
available on the 'net.  The complete list of updates will be listed in both 
the ChangeLog.txt file in this README.

Jotun's original README is README.Original

This version's home network is freenode (chat.freenode.net:6667) and the games
home channel is #idlerpgng.  There is also a general discussion channel that
we encourage you to join; this channel is #idlerpg-ng-discuss

Please come join us :)
